_sText:
Go up the elevator to get an AWP, AK47, or a M4A1.

Buttons on the left of hexagonal platform control how many dots there are.

To use this map for what it is intended for, you do what is called reps.

A rep is where you go from the center dot, to another dot then back. I recommend doing 20 reps each dot.

Idea derived from mm_delight which didn't suit my taste. Although it worked, I didn't like looking at the textures and shapes in the map which is why I made this one.
